---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Cigna Global in Vietnam', level: 2 },
  { id: 'vietnam-network', text: 'Network Coverage', level: 2 },
  { id: 'plans-and-pricing', text: 'Plans and Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-its-for', text: 'Who Should Choose Cigna', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Health Insurance in Vietnam', href: '/countries/vietnam/insurance' },
  { title: 'Cigna Global Review', href: '/providers/cigna-global' },
  { title: 'Cigna vs Allianz', href: '/compare/cigna-global-vs-allianz-care' },
];

const planColumns = [
  { key: 'plan', header: 'Plan' },
  { key: 'coverage', header: 'Coverage' },
  { key: 'vnPrice', header: 'Vietnam (Age 35)' },
];

const planRows = [
  { plan: 'Silver', coverage: 'Inpatient + Day-patient', vnPrice: '$110-150/mo' },
  { plan: 'Gold', coverage: 'Silver + Outpatient', vnPrice: '$150-200/mo' },
  { plan: 'Platinum', coverage: 'Gold + Enhanced', vnPrice: '$200-270/mo' },
];

const hospitalColumns = [
  { key: 'city', header: 'City' },
  { key: 'hospitals', header: 'Network Hospitals' },
  { key: 'directBilling', header: 'Direct Billing' },
];

const hospitalRows = [
  { city: 'Ho Chi Minh City', hospitals: 'FV Hospital, Vinmec Central Park, Columbia Asia', directBilling: true },
  { city: 'Hanoi', hospitals: 'Vinmec Times City, Family Medical Practice, French Hospital', directBilling: true },
  { city: 'Da Nang', hospitals: 'Vinmec Da Nang, Family Medical Practice', directBilling: true },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Cigna Global Health Insurance in Vietnam"
  description="Complete guide to using Cigna Global in Vietnam. Local network in HCMC, Hanoi, Da Nang, evacuation coverage, and pricing."
  headline="Cigna Global Health Insurance in Vietnam"
  subheadline="Comprehensive international coverage for expats in Vietnam."
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/countries/vietnam-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get a Cigna Vietnam Quote"
  ctaButtonHref="/providers/cigna-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Cigna Global in Vietnam</h2>
  <p>
    Cigna Global is a strong choice for long-term expats in Vietnam who want comprehensive coverage. With $1-3M limits, regional evacuation benefits, and direct billing at major Vietnamese hospitals, Cigna provides solid protection.
  </p>
  <p>
    Vietnam's affordable healthcare makes high premiums harder to justify for some, but for families, older expats, or anyone with health concerns, Cigna's comprehensive coverage is worth considering.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Get a Vietnam-Specific Quote"
    description="See what Cigna Global costs for expats in Vietnam."
    buttonText="Get Quote"
    buttonHref="/providers/cigna-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="vietnam-network">Network Coverage in Vietnam</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={hospitalColumns} rows={hospitalRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Key Network Points</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>HCMC:</strong> FV Hospital (top international standard), Vinmec Central Park</li>
    <li><strong>Hanoi:</strong> Vinmec Times City, French Hospital</li>
    <li><strong>Da Nang:</strong> Growing network with Vinmec coverage</li>
    <li><strong>Evacuation:</strong> Coverage to Bangkok/Singapore when needed</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="plans-and-pricing">Plans and Pricing</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={planColumns} rows={planRows} />
  </div>

  <p>
    Vietnam premiums are lower than Singapore or UAE due to lower healthcare costs. High-deductible options can reduce premiums further.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-its-for">Who Should Choose Cigna in Vietnam</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Good Fit</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
        <li>Long-term expats and families</li>
        <li>Those with health concerns</li>
        <li>Expats wanting evacuation coverage</li>
        <li>Those valuing comprehensive protection</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Consider Alternatives</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Short-term digital nomads (SafetyWing)</li>
        <li>Budget-conscious healthy expats (IMG)</li>
        <li>Those comfortable paying out of pocket</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready for Coverage in Vietnam?"
    description="Get a personalized Cigna Global quote."
    buttonText="Get Your Quote"
    buttonHref="/providers/cigna-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Verify coverage details directly with Cigna before purchasing.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
